description.content: We are a newly remodeled hotel in the heart of the Sierra Mountains. Near several ski resorts and beautiful Lake Tahoe, we are the best choice for accommodations in Truckee.  We offer a free full hot breakfast to start your day of exploration off right. Each room is furnished with the most comfortable beds in Truckee, free wireless Internet, a mini-fridge and a microwave. We are conveniently located right next door to three outstanding restaurants. The fun and activities in the Truckee area are limitless, even us locals are always finding new and exciting things to do. Come find out what makes this unique town so special and stay with the Best Western Plus Truckee-Tahoe Hotel while you are here. Enjoy your stay.

name.content: Holiday Inn Express South Lake Tahoe

description.content: Situated in South Lake Tahoe, this hotel is close to Heavenly Ski Resort and Zephyr Cove Beach. This hotel offers multilingual staff, coffee and newspapers in the lobby offers 89 rooms in total. Facilities include 24-hour reception, restaurant, Internet access, and a car park.  Guest rooms have air conditioning, an en suite bathroom, a double bed and televisions. Other amenities include a telephone, tea and coffee making facilities and Internet access. Wake-up calls are also included and all guest rooms are non-smoking.  The hotel has a heated outdoor swimming pool and a spa centre. Guests may also go horse riding, motor boating or sailing as well as Edgewood Golf Course.  The hotel has a restaurant on site offering set menu lunch and dinner. A complimentary continental breakfast is included in the rate.

From the acclaimed Still water Spa, 24-hour gaming action and Camp Hyatt to the renovated cottages and year-round heated lagoon-style pool, the Hyatt has every amenity for the discriminating traveler. description.content: Located in the heart of the Sierra Nevada, the Hotel lifestyle isn't the only thing that will keep you coming back for more. The Shops at Heavenly are a short 5-minute walk from the Hotel also one hour away is Kirkwood and it offers big mountain adventure with a down home atmosphere. Tap into the rock star inside of you with a hotel experience that brings together lavishness, quality and edge. It cranked the wow factor in every room, featuring modern amenities and facilities, picturesque views of Lake Tahoe and its alpine peaks and the kind of rock ‘n roll memorabilia you can only find at a this amazing Hotel and Casino.

Located a relatively short drive from California and Nevada, this superb property offers luxury amenities in the heart of South Lake Tahoe. The Reno-Tahoe International Airport is a 60-minute drive away and sports enthusiasts will soon remember this destination for a variety of activities. Guests will find a choice of two-bedroom suites with a welcoming atmosphere, ideal for relaxing after a long day. All suites are equipped with a spacious living room and a private bathroom with all the necessary amenities for a comfortable stay. After a day out in the mountains or on Lake Tahoe, guests and their families can dine in the warm American-style restaurant, enjoy one of the hotel's three atrium's, or take a dip in the large garden indoor heated pool. Sports enthusiasts can relax in the Jacuzzi after testing the fitness centre. Whether for business or pleasure, everything here is for an unforgettable stay.

description.content:
MontBleu is only 54 miles from the Reno/Tahoe International Airport. To help guests begin their vacation, the Tahoe resort offers various options for transportation to and from the airport.
Built on impeccable service and attention to detail, MontBleu is a mountain haven that exceeds the fondest expectations.  Enjoy a state of the art Workout Facility, indoor lagoon style pool or be pampered at the superb spa. Whatever the pleasure, MontBleu offers an extensive collection of services to make the stay the time of your life. 
Tahoe has never been known for its cuisine. That's about to change. At MontBleu, you'll find the dining experiences that rival those of world-class resorts. We're challenging chefs to set a new standard. And since an evening out usually means more than merely a fabulous meal, we have Vegas-caliber nightlife to fill the hours until sunrise.
The hotel boast 438 luxurious Lake Tahoe hotel rooms, many with spectacular lake and mountain views. Suites are designed for conferencing and entertaining, and feature a living area, big screen TV, dining and wet bar. MontBleu gives everything guests would expect from one of the premier Lake Tahoe resorts.
Enjoy the best that civilization has to offer amidst the incomparable beauty of the Sierra Nevada Mountains. Must be 21 years of age to check-in.

The hotel is located approximately 3 km from downtown Truckee, 13 km from the Northstar Tahoe Ski Resort, and 53 km from Reno-Tahoe International Airport.

Complimentary hotel amenities include hot breakfasts in the breakfast room, wireless Internet access in the lobby, ample meeting space, 24-hour coffee and tea service in the lobby, and weekday newspaper delivery. Business amenities include message and fax services at the 24-hour front desk. The hotel is air conditioned and includes a restaurant. After a day of activity, guests can relax at the outdoor pool or soothe weary muscles in the hotel's hot tub.

All rooms feature complimentary wireless Internet access, voicemail, individual climate control, hairdryer, coffeemaker, free local calls, and 32-inch TV with DVD player and satellite/cable. The en suite bathroom includes a shower/bath.

The hotel features an outdoor swimming pool and sun loungers.

The Ritz-Carlton, Lake Tahoe, situated mid-mountain in the Northstar-at-Tahoe ski area, features luxury accommodations, ski-in/out access with mountain concierge services, a signature restaurant by famed San Francisco celebrity Chef Traci Des Jardins, a 17,000 sq. ft. spa and preferred access to the Old Greenwood and Coyote Moon golf courses. Rates are inclusive of resort fee.

Halfway between Truckee and the north end of Lake Tahoe, this mountain lodge (part of the 4050 ha Northstar at Tahoe resort) is reputed to be among the best in the nation for family vacations.

The hotel has an adults-only clubhouse offers leather couches, a fireplace, and a library.

Comfortable accommodations at Northstar at Tahoe Village include rooms, studios, and multi-bedroom condos. All units offer VCRs and decks and most include a fireplace.

The hotel features a large recreation complex.

Enjoying a prime location at the base of Squaw Valley ski resort and surrounded by an impressive natural landscape, this magnificent mountain residence is a perfect base to spend a relaxing break away from the hustle and the bustle of the city and enjoy endless recreational activities during all four seasons. The property is only a 10-minute drive from the famous Lake Tahoe, while the international airport is about 70 km away. The accommodation units present a charming interior design that blends perfectly with the spectacular environment, offering an ideal place to relax after an exciting day out. Guests can choose between different dining and wining options, all prepared to the highest culinary standards and presented with attention to detail. In addition to this, a full-service spa and a complete health and fitness centre are also available on-site, providing guests an authentic world of relaxation and well-being.

This family-friendly, 4-star accommodation is situated in The Village at Northstar, offering shopping, dining, Starbucks, skating, movies and access to the slopes at Northstar California. Lake Tahoe is about a 10-minute drive away and Squaw Valley is about 30 km from the establishment.

Guests will enjoy luxurious one-, two-, three- and four-bedroom condominiums, each with a full kitchen which has a refrigerator, stove and microwave, as well as tea and coffee-making facilities. Perfect for families and children, residences have great appointments such as a large living space with a gas fireplace, the latest audio-visual equipment, cable TV, a washer/dryer, a deck or terrace with expansive mountain or Village views, air conditioning and heating. All bedrooms are ensuite with a shower, some with a bath, and hairdryer. Further in-room amenities include various bedding options (king, queen, double, bunk), sleeper sofas, a direct-dial telephone, and ironing set. Junior suites and studios are also available and include a kitchenette with full bathroom, some with a fireplace. 

Guests of this aparthotel can walk to the ski slopes and have access to heated, underground parking, a concierge, bell service (winter) and lobby with lift access. The property has a year-round, heated outdoor swimming pool, hot tubs, a steam room, game room and ski lockers. Golfing, sailing, horseback riding, and biking can be arranged for an additional fee.

description.content:
Conveniently located near Heavenly Mountain Ski Resort and other prime winter recreation areas, this hotel is situated directly across the road from beautiful Lake Tahoe. The hotel's neighbourhood includes the popular Tahoe Bowl Family Fun Center, the new Bear Beach Café and other restaurants and lounges.

This 100-room hotel offers the ideal blend of relaxation and recreation that makes family holidays, romantic getaways or even small business gatherings very special, any time of the year. The resort makes it easy to experience the Tahoe lifestyle. There are complimentary ski lockers and snowshoes available for guest use and also complimentary wireless Internet access. Complimentary parking is available at the hotel and a 24-hour front desk with concierge and express check-out are also provided. Business guests may take advantage of the meeting and banquet facilities. Further facilities available to guests at this air-conditioned club resort include a hotel safe, cloakroom, bar and a laundry service.any of the rooms and suites feature views of Lake Tahoe and the surrounding Sierras. In addition to private balconies, every room comes equipped with mini refrigerators and a microwave oven. Furthermore, all accommodation units come with a private bathroom with a shower, bathtub and hairdryer. Other standard features include a direct dial telephone, satellite/cable TV, radio and Internet access, as well as tea and coffee making facilities, an iron and ironing board, king-size bed and individually regulated air conditioning and heating units.

Guests can enjoy an outdoor swimming pool with a spa tub. Alternatively, they can work up a sweat in the sauna or head to the gym for a workout. There is a playground on site for children.

The hotel offers the Bear Beach Café. Breakfast is served each morning at the hotel and lunch and dinner may be selected from various menu options.

This beautiful hotel is located in Lake Tahoe, Nevada. It boasts a prime location close to the Edgewood Tahoe Golf Course and to Tahoe Crescent V shopping centre. Surrounded by nature, this establishment offers a warm and relaxing atmosphere providing first quality facilities. Clients will find a wide range of spacious rooms designed to suit all their needs. All of them offer two bathrooms, high speed internet access (fees may apply) and a fully-equipped private bathroom. This stunning establishment includes seven exceptional restaurants, a luxurious spa featuring the finest health and state-of-the-art beauty treatments, and the perfect atmosphere to have a great holiday with the whole family. With these world class amenities this hotel is the perfect place to stay in beautiful Lake Tahoe.

The guest rooms are sumptuously appointed, offering a haven of peace and serenity in which to escape the rest of the world. Guests will be taken aback by the unparalleled choice of facilities and services that the hotel has to offer. Guests can enjoy the vibrant casino, indulge in retail therapy or dine in style at this splendid hotel. Guests are invited to enjoy the ultimate relaxation in the spa, for the utmost in rejuvenation and invigoration.

A terrific setting is just the beginning of the rewards awaiting you at Squaw Valley Lodge. You'll enjoy amenities such as the five large whirlpools, a sauna and steam room, an outdoor pool, and tennis courts. Skiers couldn't ask for a better home base--you can ski out right from the door of your condominium.

Also nearby are Heavenly Ski Resort and Edgewood Tahoe Golf Course. Rates are inclusive of resort fee. Guests who book the Exclusive room categories will be responsible to pay the daily Resort Fee directly at the hotel.
